Notes: WIAC Tournament Championship...UWO earns WIAC's automatic bid to the NCAA
Div. III Championship...UWO defeated UWS in last year's WIAC Tournament title
game in Oshkosh...UWO gets 16 points from Kuehl, 13 from Schmidt and 11 points
and 10 rebounds from Richard...UWS gets 26 points from Linzmeier.
